    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/822cfded25505d4899f4a4232569e686.avif?t=1732025091\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>这片贫瘠的土地上，先代牛仔们都是在革命、战争和困苦之隙艰难求生。从废弃的矿井到尘封的道路，再到四周那些俯瞰着沙漠腹地的群山，Rancho del Arroyo（阿罗约牧场）延续了狂野的西部精神。面对烈日的炙烤，体验这片生机勃勃的土地，探索那些早已被人所遗忘的遗迹。   <br><br><strong>狩猎热点</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/8b05018acc396dcd22b24f6e984b0314.avif?t=1732025091\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>远眺白尾鹿、骡鹿与大角羊在平原上寻找荫蔽。去河边的话，便有机会看到格兰德火鸡。在接近环颈雉鸡、领西貒和郊狼的时候，请时刻把手指放在扳机上。当夜幕降临时，用沙漠中的灌木隐藏自己的身形，看那狡猾的墨西哥山猫悄无声息地追踪羚羊兔。<br><br><strong>COUSO MODEL 1897</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/cb7d14a7fb3fe47b1ff3ecd1fabdaf12.poster.avif?t=1732025091\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/cb7d14a7fb3fe47b1ff3ecd1fabdaf12.webm?t=1732025091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/cb7d14a7fb3fe47b1ff3ecd1fabdaf12.mp4?t=1732025091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Couso Model 1897 16号泵动式霰弹枪诞生于19世纪晚期，在猎人、警官与士兵们中间广受欢迎。它的管状弹匣能够容纳五发子弹，并且可以连续快速击发，因此在资深猎人看来，它算得上是一把能够应对多种情况的武器。<br><br><strong>纠正过去的错误</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/b670938af233be23410ff8cf1734c91b.avif?t=1732025091\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>当看护人萨尔瓦多·索托·穆尼奥斯返回自己的童年故乡，接管家族牧场时，他做出了一个将永远改变家族传承的决定，那便是卖掉牲畜并将这片土地改造成自然保护区。再过几周，这家牧场就将重新开放，萨尔瓦多想让你帮忙把这里变成一个合适的猎场。在这过程中，你将揭开尘封已久的秘密，并解开令强大家族分崩离析的世纪之谜。<br><br><strong>分享体验</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/c7beeb043d59165ffe7a1577ae50f891.poster.avif?t=1732025091\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/c7beeb043d59165ffe7a1577ae50f891.webm?t=1732025091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608440/extras/c7beeb043d59165ffe7a1577ae50f891.mp4?t=1732025091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>即使你没有此DLC，也可以加入拥有DLC玩家的多人游戏中，体验保护区中的精彩内容。你可以通过这种方式体验除故事任务之外的全部内容。",
